data.description: Nestled in the quaint town of Manila, Arkansas sits 4166 N County Road 275. This charming countryside haven features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms within the 2,051sqft +/-. There is plenty of space for the whole family with a bonus room on the second level! The allure of this property extends beyond the indoors, with a workshop, equipped with electricity, storage building, hot tub, and a storm shelter! Enjoy the serenity of country living with easy access to local amenities and Manila schools. Don’t miss the opportunity to own a piece of Arkansas' natural beauty!
